            "id": 88765,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Classes podem ter funções também, que são conhecidas como <strong>métodos</strong> quando estão dentro de uma classe. Como o método <code>bark()</code> aqui.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Virtual_Pet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;brown&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"bark\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Bark&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky = Virtual_Pet()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.bark()\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Bark\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Self",
            "id": 89349,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><code>self</code> é uma palavra-chave especial que precisamos usar dentro da definição da nossa classe. Passamos <code>self</code> como o primeiro parâmetro para todos os métodos que adicionamos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Virtual_Pet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;brown&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"bark\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Bark&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky = Virtual_Pet()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.bark()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"if\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"while\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Bark\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>self</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Self",
            "id": 88784,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usamos <code>self</code> como um parâmetro nos métodos da classe para que possamos acessar as variáveis da classe como <code>color</code> e <code>legs</code> dentro dos métodos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Virtual_Pet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;brown&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  legs = \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"bark\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Bark&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display_color\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.color)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display_legs\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.legs)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky = Virtual_Pet()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.display_color()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.display_legs()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"123\" endIndex=\"127\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"brown\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>self</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Self",
            "id": 89350,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Dentro de <code>display_color()</code>, <code>self.color</code> é como acessamos o valor da variável de classe <code>color = \"brown\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Virtual_Pet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;brown&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  legs = \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"bark\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Bark&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display_color\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.color)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display_legs\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.legs)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky = Virtual_Pet()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.display_color()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.display_legs()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"123\" endIndex=\"127\" /><option startIndex=\"127\" endIndex=\"128\" /><option startIndex=\"128\" endIndex=\"133\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"brown\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>self</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e finalmente <code>color</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Self",
            "id": 89351,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Sem usar <code>self</code> não seríamos capazes de acessar as variáveis da classe, pois elas são declaradas fora do escopo do método da classe.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Virtual_Pet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;brown&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  legs = \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"bark\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Bark&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display_color\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.color)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"display_legs\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.legs)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky = Virtual_Pet()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.display_color()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky.display_legs()\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"brown\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"4\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
